description:
Over 1900 satisfied students

This course titled as "Understand Router commands in 1 hr for CCNA CCNP students" is about understanding the cisco commands of routers and switches.

Students will see video sessions of cisco routers with all important commands along with explanation of output.

GNS3 has been used for making you take feel of cisco router Command Line Interface.

This course is of 1 hour time which includes 5 main videos plus one Promo Video!!!

It has been divided in to 5 parts of 4-6 commands each starting from the basic ones to little advance level.

Students of CCNA and CCNP who are aspiring to enhance their troubleshooting and Configuration skills will get good understanding of CLI , therefore, It will benefit them :-)

Student who will buy this course will get special discount on my new courses..
title: Understand Router commands in 1 hr for CCNA CCNP students
